quran[56]{c,v,t}:
  74,1,Wewe wipfutse amahuzu
  74,2,Haguruka utuze abantu
  74,3,Uninahaze Umuremyi wawe
  74,4,Usukure n’impuzu zawe
  74,5,N’amabi yose ntuyiteho
  74,6,"Kandi\tntugire\tineza\tkubiremwa\tkugira\tngo\turonke\tumusesekara w’amaronko ngaha kw’isi"
  74,7,"Kubera Umuremyi wawe, wewe niwigumye gusa"
  74,8,Niha vuzwa inzamba y’umuhero w’isi
  74,9,Kuri uwo musi uzoba ari umusi uhambaye cane
  74,10,"Kubahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, uwo musi ntuzoba woroshe kuribo namba"
  74,11,Jewe n’undeke hamwe nuwo niremeye jewe nyene
  74,12,Ndamuhezagire aronke amatungo menshi
  74,13,N’ibibondo biboneka ahariho hose
  74,14,Ndamugirira ibintu vyiwe neza cane
  74,15,Hanyuma yizera yuko nzomwongereza
  74,16,Oya! Mu vy’ukuri yahora ahakana amajambo yacu meranda
  74,17,Rero nzo muhana n’ibihano bininiya cane
  74,18,Mu vy’ukuri yariyumviriye n’ugupima
  74,19,"Arahonywa, none ni gute yateguye mugutyoza iyi Qur’ani"
  74,20,"Kandi yarahonejwe, none ni gute yateguye mugutyoza iyi Qur’ani"
  74,21,Hanyuma yaritegereje
  74,22,Hanyuma arazinga mumaso yiwe kugeza naho haboneka iminkanyari
  74,23,Hanyuma ukuri aguha umugongo wiwe n’ukwishima cane
  74,24,"N’ukuvuga ati:- ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari uburozi bwabuwe"
  74,25,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari amajambo y’umuntu asanzwe
  74,26,Ubu vuba nzomuta mu muriro udahera
  74,27,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo muriro udahera
  74,28,Udasigaza nico usigaza
  74,29,Uwo muriro nuwu babura urukoba rimwe na rimwe
  74,30,Hejuru yuwo muriro udahera hariho abawucungera bashika kw’icumi n’icenda
  74,31,"Ntitwashizeho abacungera uwo muriro udahera atari abamarayika, kandi ntitwagize igitigiri cabo cumi n’icenda atari uko ari ikibazo kuri barya bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri kugira ngo bashirwe n’abahawe ibitabu imbere yanyu, n’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bagumane ukwemera kwabo, kandi ntibagire amakenga bamwe bahawe igitabu imbere yanyu canke aba Isilamu n’abazoba bafise indwara mu mitima yabo hamwe n’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri baze bavuge bati:- Imana yashatse kugira iki kuri kano karorero? Uku rero niko Imana ireka umuntu akazimira kuwo yishakiye n’ukurongora uwo yishakiye, kandi nta numwe afise ubumenyi bw’ukumenya ingabo z’Umuremyi wawe atariyo yonyene gusa, kandi ntivyari kuba atari ikimenyetso kubiremwa vyose"
  74,32,Sivyo none ? Ndarahiye k’ukwezi
  74,33,N’Ijoro rikeye
  74,34,No mugitondo hakeye
  74,35,Mu vy’ukuri uwo muriro udahera n’umwe mungorane niniya zihambaye cane
  74,36,N’igabisho ku bantu
  74,37,K’uwushaka muri mwebwe n’atanguze kuja imbere canke aje inyuma
  74,38,"Umutima\tw’umwumwe\twese\tuzo\tkwugaranirwa\tmu\tmuriro\tudahera kubera ibikorwa bibi wakoze"
  74,39,Dukuye mwo abantu b’iburyo
  74,40,Abo bantu bazoba mu mirima babazanya
  74,41,Kubera abantu babi
  74,42,N’ikintu nyabaki cabatwaye mu muriro udahera
  74,43,"Bazo vuga bati:- ntitwari mu bantu bahora basenga"
  74,44,Kandi ntitwahora duha abakene ibifungugwa
  74,45,Kandi twahora twibira mu bicumuro hamwe n’abahora bibira
  74,46,Kandi twahora duhakana yuko ata musi w’uguciribwa imanza
  74,47,Kugeza n’aho dushikirwa n’urupfu
  74,48,Ntaco bizofasha uko gusaba kw’abasabira abaribo bose
  74,49,Mbega bafise iki ? Ntibitaho kuri rino tuza
  74,50,Nkuko umengo n’indogobwe zigenda ningoga na ningoga
  74,51,Ziruka nk’intare
  74,52,"Umwe wese muribo\tagomba yuko ahabwa impapuro zizoba zanditswe ko"
  74,53,Oya! kuri bo ntibatinya umuhero w’Isi
  74,54,"Oya ! Si uko, mu vy’ukuri ubwo n’ubwibutso"
  74,55,Rero uwushaka azokwibuka
  74,56,"Ntibazo kwibuka atari uko Imana yabishatse, kuko niyo ikwiwe gutinywa n’ukugira imbabazi"